betterquesting:10.desc:8:
Your first destination! Absolutely chock full of lithium, quartz, and most importantly, your first source of nickel to start producing stainless steel for space-grade machinery. The Mun is the first atmosphere-less body available in a regular playthrough, necessary for making the first tier of drive processors in the vacuum solderer.

The B-Side destination alternative to the Mun, Minmus is characterized by a distinctive mint-choc-chip ice-cream aesthetic. Pumps function here, but instead of producing water, this moon bizarrely produces milk, allowing for full automation of butter, milkshakes and ice-cream.
